tes that Substack hosts =E2=80=9Canti-vaccine pseudo-science, Covid conspir=
acy theories and other material that is generally restricted on mainstream =
social networks=E2=80=9D. It=E2=80=99s not clear if that includes =E2=80=9C=
You can still get COVID after the vaccine=E2=80=9D or =E2=80=9CIt=E2=80=99s=
 very possible that COVID was a lab leak=E2=80=9D, both of which were in so=
me form or another banned or demoted on various social networks for being a=
nti-vaccine pseudo-science and a Covid conspiracy theory. In other words, f=
ree speech does still matter, even if no one wants to be in a Nazi bar.

